These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts, drama, action
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, helicopter, scooter, snowmobile
1. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the helicopter and the person driving the scooter##2
6. the person watching action movies is the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | action | epic     | drama | martial-arts |
| Transport     | boat     | scooter | snowmobile  | helicopter      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, disco, metal, trance
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, skateboard, subway, quad-bike
1. the fan of disco is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of trance is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the fan of metal is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | funk | disco    | trance     | metal  |
| Transport     | tram    | subway | skateboard | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, gospel, folk, hip-hop
4 different pets are kept: mouse, hedgehog, pony, turtle
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
2. the fan of gospel is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
5. the owner of the pony is on the right of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | folk   | funk  | hip-hop |
| Pet           | hedgehog | turtle | pony | mouse  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, drawing, filmmaking, puzzles
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, british, spanish, mexican
1. the mexican is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the spanish##2
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
4. the spanish is on the left or right of the mexican##3
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
6. the japanese is on the right of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | drawing | magic-tricks | puzzles | filmmaking  |
| Nationality   | british  | japanese   | mexican  | spanish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, sprite, coffee, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, writing, sudoku, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | sprite   | coffee | tea    |
| Hobby      | writing | collecting | sudoku       | traveling |

