.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, cola, sprite, hot-chocolate
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, car, snowmobile, ship
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the ship and the person drinking sprite##2
3. the person driving the van is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person drinking lemonade##2
4. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | lemonade | sprite | hot-chocolate | cola |
| Transport   | car | van  | snowmobile    | ship  |

