2. the italian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
4. the nigerian is between the australian and the russian##2
5. the person driving the subway is the person driving the subway##1
6. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the tram and the russian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | italian | russian | nigerian | australian     |
| Transport     | boat | jet-ski  | subway   | tram |

