.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, camping, magic-tricks, dancing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, comedy, zombie, sports
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby         | dancing | magic-tricks | writing | camping   |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | zombie | thriller      | sports |

