.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, cat, frog, bird
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, surfing, ice-hockey, skateboarding
1. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the owner of the bird##1
4. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
5. the owner of the rat is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the cat is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | rat | cat   | frog      | bird      |
| Sport   | surfing     | ice-hockey | lacrosse | skateboarding |

