.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, techno, blues, country
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, brazilian, colombian, german
1. the dutch is on the right of the brazilian##1
2. the fan of blues is between the german and the brazilian##2
3. the fan of techno is the brazilian##1
4. the colombian is on the left of the brazilian##1
5. the fan of country is on the left or right of the dutch##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | techno | blues      | country   |
| Nationality   | colombian  | brazilian    | dutch | german |

