.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, traveling, rock-climbing, drawing
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, bus, airplane, train
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person driving the train is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
5. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
6. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby       | gardening | rock-climbing | drawing    | traveling      |
| Transport   | airplane       | train       | bus | scooter |

