2. the australian is the australian##1
3. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
4. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the japanese##3
5. the mexican is on the left or right of the spanish##3
6. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the spanish##3
7. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the pony##1

