.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, peas, zucchini, peach
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, accountant, nurse, designer
1. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the accountant##3
2. the accountant is on the right of the nurse##1
3. the person eating peas is on the left of the dancer##1
4. the accountant is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating zucchini is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food   | peas  | broccoli | peach  | zucchini      |
| Job    | designer | dancer | nurse | accountant |

