4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, horse, rabbit, frog
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person watching epic movies is the owner of the frog##1
3. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the owner of the rabbit is between the person watching time-travel movies and the owner of the frog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | epic  | crime  | time-travel |
| Pet           | chinchilla    | frog | rabbit | horse |

