2. the librarian is on the left or right of the journalist##3
3. the analyst is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
4. the journalist is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
5. the journalist is on the left of the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1        |      2       |   3    |   4    |
| Food   | asparagus        | mango       | grapes   | watermelon |
