.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, coffee, lemonade, juice
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, rugby, skateboarding, cycling
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
7. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | coffee     | tea     | lemonade          | juice |
| Sport      | volleyball | rugby | cycling | skateboarding  |

 